    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handstand Hank 是一次惩罚性的体验，将考验你的耐心，当你试图穿越一座障碍山时。跳跃、跌倒和愤怒，战胜越来越难的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308150/extras/4e0ca010483a12037bfd49dd49d5f8e7.poster.avif?t=1750490610\" width=616 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308150/extras/4e0ca010483a12037bfd49dd49d5f8e7.webm?t=1750490610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308150/extras/4e0ca010483a12037bfd49dd49d5f8e7.mp4?t=1750490610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >准备迎接挑战：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4个极其艰难的区域——每个区域都带来新的独特挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两种玩法 - 具有检查点的简单模式或每次跌倒代价巨大的困难模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无与伦比的胜利等待着登顶者。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308150/extras/f3ef56ec9242f809eaf057f8a90732f0.webp?t=1750490610\" width=616 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308150/extras/95a52ae14beb06068e42a5a38e104688.poster.avif?t=1750490610\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308150/extras/95a52ae14beb06068e42a5a38e104688.webm?t=1750490610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3308150/extras/95a52ae14beb06068e42a5a38e104688.mp4?t=1750490610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
